ges/Gemini.svg" alt="Gemini"> <img class="img-scroll" src="/assets/images/OpenAI.svg" alt="GPT"> <img class="img-scroll" src="/assets/images/Claude.svg" alt="Claude"> </div> </div> </div> </section>
